{"tid":262312,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"深水埗洋漢涉強姦女子被捕 (08:50)","createTime":"2017-05-29T06:41:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T06:47:04.000Z","uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"759c4724ffeda164765b4dd54969cdf02ced3c83","tid":262312,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:41:01.000Z","msg":"深水埗發生強姦案。一名37歲女子昨在區內一單位懷疑被同齡洋漢Pham強姦，於是報警，人員接報到場，Pham涉案被捕，案件交由深水埗警區刑事調查隊第1隊跟進。 - See more at: <a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170529/s00001/1496018107401#sthash.VlXsoVjq.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170529%2Fs00001%2F1496018107401%23sthash.VlXsoVjq.dpuf&d=%2B4z7xIHEW9mqiOB01FK1eviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=69fe57ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170529%2Fs00001%2F1496018107401%23sthash.VlXsoVjq.dpuf&h=808a03c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170529/s00001/1496018107401#sthash.VlXsoVjq.dpuf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有洋腸食仲報驚？"},{"pid":"7043af83837c21258dd0c6a350560e86e180a590","tid":262312,"uid":10680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:45:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c0476b185ddecee6ddd995346fe3ed31a48e862","tid":262312,"uid":102132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:46:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b92ab4e3c3df95489d3f8f0b123d42ac2aff17a","tid":262312,"uid":340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:47:04.000Z","msg":"深水埗發生強姦案，凌晨零時許，警方接獲一名37歲越南籍女子報案，指她昨日在元州街內一單位疑遭一名<span style=\"color: red;\">越南籍同鄉</span>強姦。警員接報到場調查，以涉嫌強姦，拘捕一名持「行街紙」留港的37歲越南籍男子PHAM，帶署扣查，案件交深水埗警區刑事調查隊跟進。"}]}